Today was the start of new chapter in my journey -  I taught my first, of hopefully many, college courses! 
@dr.andrew.hanna and I kicked off week one of our 4 week, pop up UNL class facilitated at The Bay. This course shows students how to apply design thinking/tools to their lives, helping them tackle one of life’s toughest questions, “what do you want to do next?” 🤔 
This is one of my favorite conversations to have and getting to bring it to the youth in my community in such a valuable way is the best part. I can’t wait to see where this goes, where all my colleges at 👀 🚀

📸 - @nebraskac4e

Sometimes all it takes is a cold can of water on a hot summer night to make someones face light up or that shared moment in a fist bump over fresh pair of socks. Every item we drop isn’t just a supply, it’s a little boost of hope, or a small whisper that says ‘you matter, someone cares, keep going‘ Its that little drop of unexpected kindness that I’ve seen spark incredible change in people. So as the summer temperatures keep rising & you’re at the store trying to murder your thirst, scoop up an extra can or two of @liquiddeath to spread some much needed positive vibes in your community 💧🛹 #MurderYourThirst #SkateForChange @LiquidDeath @skateforchange

Big cheers to our principal, Dr. James Blake, and @thebay_  as we celebrate two incredible wins! 🎉 We’re humbled to receive the award for Outstanding Contributions by an Organization, and thrilled that Dr. Blake’s dedication, innovative leadership, and quick problem-solving have earned him the honor of Outstanding Contribution by an Administrator. 

Our partnership with Lincoln Public Schools at @bayhighlnk is a testament to the power of creative collaboration and relentless commitment to our students’ futures. Dr. Blake’s visionary leadership and tireless dedication have been instrumental in navigating these uncharted waters. ⛵️ 

To every partner, believer, and supporter who has been part of our journey, we offer our heartfelt gratitude. 🙏 Your trust in us has played an integral role in turning Bay High from a dream into a thriving reality. 

These accolades serve as a beautiful reminder of how far we’ve come, but the real reward is seeing the impact we’re making together, every day, in the lives of our students. We believe in the transformative power of creativity and innovation in education - and today, we’re more committed than ever to inspire and shape the next generation of creative thinkers. Let’s continue to raise the tide and create waves of change together. 🤝 #WeAreBayHig #BayHighLNK #Bandits
